sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User<br/>(nvsnap freeze / API)
    participant Srv as nvsnap-server
    participant Agent as nvsnap-agent<br/>(node N1)
    participant WL as Workload Pod
    participant Lib as libnvsnap_intercept.so
    participant CRIU as CRIU
    participant CC as cuda-checkpoint
    participant PVC as per-capture PVC
    participant Blob as nvsnap-blobstore

    User->>Srv: POST /checkpoint/pod {pod, ns}
    Srv->>Agent: Checkpoint(pod, ns, ckptID)
    Agent->>WL: discover PIDs via cgroup
    Agent->>WL: SIGUSR1 (quiesce)
    WL->>Lib: signal handler
    Lib->>Lib: drain io_uring queues
    Lib->>Lib: ncclCommAbort all comms<br/>(multi-GPU only)
    Lib->>WL: marker /dev/shm/nvsnap-quiesce-done-<pid>
    Agent->>WL: poll for quiesce marker (30s timeout)

    Agent->>CC: snapshot GPU state
    CC-->>Agent: nvidia-files.img
    Agent->>CRIU: dump --tree=<root-pid> --external=dev[195/0]:nvidia0 ...
    CRIU->>WL: ptrace seize all threads
    CRIU->>WL: dump memory, fds, vmas to /var/lib/containerd/nvsnap-checkpoints/<id>/
    CRIU-->>Agent: dump complete (1237 files for NIM 8B)

    Agent->>Agent: rootfs delta capture<br/>(if enabled)
    Agent->>PVC: write CRIU + rootfs artifacts
    Agent->>Blob: upload chunks (content-addressed)
    Agent->>Srv: POST /api/v1/checkpoints/register
    Srv-->>User: 202 Accepted {ckptID, size, location}

    Note over Agent,Blob: NIM 8B: 76 GB checkpoint, ~3 min total
